    "[31] conducted a research that investigates the relationship between BLEU, ROUGE, and METEOR metrics and human assessments.",
    "The study reveals a weak association, particularly for BLEU.",
    "METEOR has the powerful connection, however it still falls somewhat short of true human judgments.",
    "Another approach to evaluate is using human review services such as CrowdFlower or Amazon Mechanical Turks.",
    "These models utilize numerous criteria like as relevancy, completeness, readability, correctness, and human likeness."
  ]
